data.description: Welcome to this stunning West Bloomington home. This home is truly move in ready. The home flows from the generous foyer to the main floor with a stunning open kitchen with granite counter tops and stainless-steel appliances with a breakfast bar. The ample great room is a fantastic place to entertain. The main floor also has a lovely sun room just off the kitchen, a bedroom that is currently being used as an office and a ¾ bathroom. Just a few stairs down from the kitchen is the family room that walks out to the patio and fenced in back yard. All of the three bathrooms in the home have been fully remodeled with gorgeous tile work throughout. The primary suite has a walk-in closet and beautiful ¾ bath. Two additional bedrooms and a full bath complete the upper level. The basement has a rec room and work out space, along with plenty of storage. This home really has it all—updates, a modern layout and a private backyard. Don’t miss!
